# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a prominent harvard child psychiatrist will curtail activities financed by the drug industry while massachusetts general hospital investigates his failure for years to disclose the consulting fees he received from drugmakers .
# ::alignments
(c / curtail-01
      :ARG0 (p / psychiatrist
            :mod (c2 / child)
            :mod (p2 / prominent)
            :location (u / university
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Harvard")))
      :ARG1 (a / activity-06
            :ARG1-of (f / finance-01
                  :ARG0 (ii / industry
                        :mod (d / drug))))
      :time (ii2 / investigate-01
            :ARG0 (h / hospital
                  :mod (g / general)
                  :location (s / state
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Massachusetts")))
            :ARG1 (f2 / fail-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (d2 / disclose-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (f3 / fee
                              :mod (c3 / consult-01)
                              :ARG1-of (r / receive-01
                                    :ARG0 p
                                    :ARG2 (c4 / company
                                          :ARG0-of (m / make-01
                                                :ARG1 (d3 / drug))))))
                  :duration (m2 / multiple
                        :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (y / year))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :op2 "Lanka"))

                  :value 1)
            :location (t3 / tea)
            :time (d / day
                  :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                        :value 2)
                  :part-of (t4 / test-01
                        :ARG1 t
                        :mod (c / cricket)
                        :location (s / stadium
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Cazaly")
                              :location (h / here))

                              :weekday (s2 / saturday)))))
      :ARG2 (s3 / score-entity
            :op1 1
            :op2 1))

                              :op1 "Israel"))

                        :mod (c3 / country

                                    :op1 "Palestine"))))

                  :mod (m2 / military
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Air"
                              :op2 "Force")
                        :mod (c4 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
            :purpose (t3 / thing
                  :ARG4-of (s / step-01
                        :ARG2 (s2 / settle-02)
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1)
                        :ARG1-of (h / hopeful-03)))))

            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (s2 / state-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)))
      :ARG1 (r / record-01
            :ARG0 (c / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "zaire"))
            :ARG1 (ii / increase-01
                  :ARG1 (o / output
                        :mod (d / diamond))
                  :ARG1-of (s3 / significant-02))
            :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG1 (b / bring-01
                        :ARG0 ii
                        :ARG1 (m / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d2 / dollar)
                              :mod (c3 / country
                                    :name n
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States")))
                  :ARG2 (p / purse
                        :mod (p2 / public))
                  :ARG3 (p3 / produce-01
                        :ARG1 (s4 / stone
                              :mod (p4 / precious)))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))
